text: Lara Villata (born 19 April 1967) is an Italian equestrian. She competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics, the 1996 Summer Olympics and the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Italian female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Italy Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Turin
